{"tid":287253,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"試着說：「牌子」 不要說：「品牌」","createTime":"2017-06-17T09:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T08:37:10.000Z","uid":38071,"like":47,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b5ba70c3bc80b484bb6ec68f8f78b44f68793b2","tid":287253,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:19:59.000Z","msg":"眼見品牌依個字越嚟越常用，單靠留comment屌都毫無作用，實在係睇唔過眼。有啲人甚至反駁話品牌係書面語牌子係口語。咁我自己就查過下屋企啲七八九十年代香港出版嘅字典，包括漢英同英漢字典，清一色唔見品牌，得牌子（或者連牌子都無，得牌號）。<br />\n<br />\n見隔離個post推得咁快，我又出個post喚起下大家關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw, 之前字典我有影低相，不過要搵搵，有人不服來辯我先up上嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464255fc94fb1d4b9ac246d97ef6db019a9074de","tid":287253,"uid":77492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:20:52.000Z","msg":"牌子"},{"pid":"aeab001ae5c12d573aa7c521e89196cfcbfbc2c7","tid":287253,"uid":38071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:24:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牌子</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffc122257904121a9269ff7b19dda77610887b4","tid":287253,"uid":38071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096143bad0b59b192a5750e2c5b60333430e93af","tid":287253,"uid":13025,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港語達人"},{"pid":"422abf644658b53d87756bbde9db5a2b2368cbaa","tid":287253,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:16:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">不服來辯</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7255f656b82d65e283abafea316325958a70365","tid":287253,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:17:55.000Z","msg":"蝗語滲入post，大家見一個block一個。"},{"pid":"59ec4519c5ade970d6bbfc5c3cce579dfb2683eb","tid":287253,"uid":34154,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"試下講：「試下講XXX, 唔好講YYY」, 唔好講：「試着說XXX, 不要說YYY」"},{"pid":"8172ffc94d432e83897f136eb47eab2c162b76fa","tid":287253,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">不服來辯</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 <br />\n我以為係波台啲9upper用詞 <br />\nGoogle過發現原來台灣大陸都有用 <br />\n咁似乎係嗰邊傳過嚟嘅<br />\n<br />\n收返對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3cf26e04a4cdc3702749c3dde731694a826741","tid":287253,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T10:39:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下講：「試下講XXX, 唔好講YYY」, 唔好講：「試着說XXX, 不要說YYY」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28612110767f0aec6c54bc9cdce1c1a71bc69bc2","tid":287253,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3518eb85e7db923fb4c087868ff71f0c2702619c","tid":287253,"uid":43308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2e7827661b013b43dc2d27f62953fa6baf05188","tid":287253,"uid":10100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:39:43.000Z","msg":"品牌同牌子好似跟本係兩種唔同用法......"},{"pid":"98a77a8bafb09ffe93dcda2396d336a3f307574a","tid":287253,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:15:34.000Z","msg":"試下講「試下講」唔好講「試著說」"},{"pid":"41ce97d322b5c435939ba79ea33c853b4ab29ba0","tid":287253,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f512e9c9fd5241485b64173c9d28e979bb314899","tid":287253,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T16:11:09.000Z","msg":"緊係講字號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177fcbfe25fd7b77f7f85ef574961c3627f5575c","tid":287253,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T19:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪戇撚尻架屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n咁「品牌效應」你叫「牌子效應」?<br />\n<br />\n[名詞+字] 呢個combination根本就係北京話特色, 「品牌」先反而符合粵語少用虛詞嘅特性<br />\n(唯一例外係「老媽子」)<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味唔識就唔好出來扮代表啦</blockquote><br />\n咁我會覺得牌子同老媽字都係例外 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拿，講真乜你覺得以前係用開品牌依個講法咩咩？我印象中品牌最多係近七八年先開始講。嘗試過google search，可惜同大陸網啲result撈埋咗一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似唔work，所以我先查字典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw, 好似上邊巴打話齋，講開名牌效應架嘛"},{"pid":"836f68333e0b906558e4ec5dfb2f1aa72af06e8d","tid":287253,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T19:29:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>緊係講字號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359e937e98aa88b4eb7af08d8e38830e6f0210f3","tid":287253,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T19:40:32.000Z","msg":"支持樓主"},{"pid":"adcdba08aadb8a670c6d245d287514e6f1f8667e","tid":287253,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>品牌同牌子好似跟本係兩種唔同用法......</blockquote><br />\n有啲用法牌子的確取代唔到品牌<br />\n但講緊嘅係品牌係大陸傳嚟嘅講法，而且大部份以前會寫牌子嘅地方都變曬品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}